data.value: This software comprises of two main features which are embeded in the software. Accurate functionality of a video player is attached along the line, with a music player. Enjoy the flow of music easily and at the same time watch movies conveniently. A voice assitant feature is attached along line with other features. The main objective of this software to merge the video player fuctionality and music player functionality in a particular software. This software can be used at various leisure period.
